1. *Muškarca* je pomogao deci da pređu ulicu. (The man helped the children to cross the street.)

2. *Muškarci* su uglavnom odgovorni za svoje porodice. (Men are usually responsible for their families.)

3. On je učinio sve što je mogao da zaštiti *muškarcu*. (He did all he could to protect the man.)

4. Ona je zainteresovana za *muškarce* sa kojima deli interese. (She is interested in men with whom she shares interests.)

5. *Muškarac* je postao poznat po svojoj hrabrosti. (The man became famous for his courage.)